{
  "texts": [
    "(GDPR) 2016 Not specific to insurance, but crucial for data privacy.",
    "A regulation on data protection and privacy for individuals within the European Union and the European Economic Area.",
    "It addresses the transfer of personal data outside the EU and EEA areas.",
    "(IDD) 2016 A European Union directive that aims to create a level playing field for all participants involved in the selling of insurance products.",
    "It enhances consumer protection and harmonizes insurance distribution rules across the EU."
  ]
}